</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:50
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='759581' id='t-759581'>But his life changed</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='762109' id='t-762109'>when he got the chance to be resettled</span>
