<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='777868' id='t-777868'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:14
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='783829' id='t-783829'>I spoke to him on Skype the other day,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='786243' id='t-786243'>and he was in his new university in Florida</span>
