<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:38
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='807655' id='t-807655'>So I want to take you back to Hany.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='810939' id='t-810939'>When I told him I was going to have the chance</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='813160' id='t-813160'>to speak to you here on the TED stage,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='815877' id='t-815877'>he allowed me to read you a poem</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='818172' id='t-818172'>that he sent in an email to me.</span>
