</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:52
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='821532' id='t-821532'>He wrote:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='825270' id='t-825270'>&quot;I miss myself,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='827830' id='t-827830'>my friends,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='830335' id='t-830335'>times of reading novels or writing poems,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='834590' id='t-834590'>birds and tea in the morning.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='839515' id='t-839515'>My room, my books, myself,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='844464' id='t-844464'>and everything that was making me smile.</span>
