</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:30
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='859323' id='t-859323'>So here is my point:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='861551' id='t-861551'>Not investing in refugees</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='863597' id='t-863597'>is a huge missed opportunity.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='869241' id='t-869241'>Leave them abandoned,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='871092' id='t-871092'>and they risk exploitation and abuse,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='876439' id='t-876439'>and leave them unskilled and uneducated,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='879712' id='t-879712'>and delay by years the return</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='882265' id='t-882265'>to peace and prosperity in their countries.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='888115' id='t-888115'>I believe how we treat the uprooted</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='891399' id='t-891399'>will shape the future of our world.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='895972' id='t-895972'>The victims of war can hold the keys</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='898926' id='t-898926'>to lasting peace,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='901447' id='t-901447'>and it's the refugees</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='903256' id='t-903256'>who can stop the cycle of violence.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:17
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='906923' id='t-906923'>Hany is at a tipping point.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='909944' id='t-909944'>We would love to help him go to university</span>
